import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { OrderDetailsService } from 'src/app/services/order-details.service'; @Component({ selector: 'app-product', templateUrl: './product.component.html' }) export class ProductComponent implements OnInit { constructor(private service:OrderDetailsService) { } foodData:any; ngOnInit(): void { this.foodData = this.service.foodDetails; } } My Projects

My Projects

Project 1: Kasanova

Kasanova project was a e-commerce website and I had to work on login page and newsletter subscription other then that I also had worked on PDP page api

Project 2: Automotive

Automotive store was an e-commerce website for auto parts. I had work for migration from m1 to m2. Also worked to fix issues on m2 site like slider issue, PDP page part checker issue, Brand list and other.

Project 2: Ann Spoyer

Ann spoyer project is an e-commerce website for designer cloth. In this project, This was started from scratch. I had to work on customize PDP, make custom API for customer,PLP and PDP. I helped client understand how magento site can be maintained like adding products, managing orders.
